com.intel.fightclub.dialog.logging.util

Interface ObjectPool.Spawn<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of object being wrapped.
    Enclosing class:
    ObjectPool<E>

    public static interface ObjectPool.Spawn<E>
    Interface for an Object that is generated by a ObjectPool instance. Typically, implementations of this interface will not be threadsafe since there is no guarantee that the object being wrapped is immutable or thread safe on its own. Therefore, care must be taken to ensure that instances are properly used in a safe manner across threads.
